{"word":"Ehud","slug":"ehud","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ehud</b> <a href=\"#/H164\">H164</a><br/><a href=\"#/H261\">H261</a> <br/> 1. A descendant of Benjamin<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=6'>1Ch 8:6</a> <br/> - Called Ehi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=21'>Gen 46:21</a> <br/> - Probably identical with:<br/> b ahiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=38'>Num 26:38</a><br/> b aharah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=1'>1Ch 8:1</a><br/> b ahoah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=4'>1Ch 8:4</a><br/> b ahiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=7'>1Ch 8:7</a><br/> b aher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=12'>1Ch 7:12</a><br/> 2. Son of Bilhan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=10'>1Ch 7:10</a><br/> 3. A Benjamite, the assassin of Eglon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=16'>Jdg 3:16</a>"}]}